AU container output is not historically implemented. Although AU is enumerated
and BlockWriteManager passes AU to SndFileEncoder, src/fweelin_block.cc's
SndFileEncoder constructor selects SF_FORMAT_FLAC only for FLAC and selects
SF_FORMAT_WAV | SF_FORMAT_FLOAT for every other value (including AU). Capturing
an .au file would therefore fabricate AU support: its bytes would be WAV/RIFF.
